{"word":"G3918 - πάρειμι - páreimi - par'-i-mee - Come","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πάρειμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">páreimi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par'-i-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வா"},{"paragraph":"1. to be by, be at hand, to have arrived, to be present"},{"paragraph":"2. to be ready, in store, at command"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee'/1510\">G1510</a> (including its various forms); to <i>be near</i>, that is, <i>at hand</i>; neuter present participle (singular) <i>time being</i>, or (plural) <i>property:</i> - come, X have, be here, + lack, (be here) present.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3918/3918\">G3918</a>, <a href=\"#/G3952/3952\">G3952</a>"}]}